  "Description": {
    "English": "A pungent atmospheric <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas</span>. High concentrations are extremely hazardous to organic life.<br><br>With the aid of <span class=\"name name-technology\">specialized machinery</span>, can be extracted from the atmospheres of <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Scorched</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Desert</span> planets.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "大气中一种刺鼻的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。如果其浓度过高，对有机物来说是十分危险的。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">专用装置</span>的帮助下，可以从<span class=\"name name-fuel\">炽热</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">沙漠</span>星球上的大气中将气体抽取出来。",
    "TencentChinese": "大气中一种刺鼻的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。如果其浓度过高，对有机物来说是十分危险的。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">专用装置</span>的帮助下，可以从<span class=\"name name-fuel\">炽热</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">沙漠</span>星球上的大气中将气体抽取出来。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "氣味強烈的大氣<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氣體</span>。濃度高時，對有機生命極度有害。<br><br>若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">專門機器</span>，可從<span class=\"name name-fuel\">炙熱</span>與<span class=\"name name-special\">沙漠</span>的星球大氣中萃取到。"
  },
